Package org.agilewiki.utils.immutable.collections

Versioned and non-versioned immutable virtual maps of lists with smart re-serialization and lazy de-serialization.

Versioned and non-versioned immutable virtual maps of lists with smart re-serialization and lazy de-serialization.
